            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "The receptionist's behavior is quite unpleasant; she doesn't know how to greet or communicate properly. If the receptionist acts this way, I can only imagine the attitude of the school principal. Having good infrastructure alone doesn't make a school great; it's the staff that truly matters.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
